Types

Aesthetics = object
  x*: Option[Scale]
  y*: Option[Scale]
  fill*: Option[Scale]
  color*: Option[Scale]
  size*: Option[Scale]
  shape*: Option[Scale]

ScaleKind = enum
  scLinearData, scTransformedData, scColor, scFillColor, scShape, scSize
PositionKind = enum
  pkIdentity = "identity", pkStack = "stack", pkDodge = "dodge", pkFill = "fill"
StatKind = enum
  stIdentity = "identity", stCount = "count", stBin = "bin"
DiscreteKind = enum
  dcDiscrete, dcContinuous
ScaleValue = object
  case kind*: ScaleKind
  of scLinearData, scTransformedData:
      val*: Value

  of scFillColor, scColor:
      color*: Color

  of scShape:
      marker*: MarkerKind

  of scSize:
      size*: float

  
SecondaryAxis = object
  trans*: Option[FormulaNode]
  name*: string
  axKind*: AxisKind

ScaleTransform = proc (v: Value): Value
Scale = object
  col*: string
  name*: string
  ids*: set[uint16]
  vKind*: ValueKind
  case scKind*: ScaleKind
  of scLinearData, scTransformedData:
      axKind*: AxisKind
      trans*: ScaleTransform
      secondaryAxis*: Option[SecondaryAxis]

  else:
    nil
  case dcKind*: DiscreteKind
  of dcDiscrete:
      valueMap*: OrderedTable[Value, ScaleValue]
      labelSeq*: seq[Value]

  of dcContinuous:
      dataScale*: ginger.Scale
      mapData*: proc (idxs: seq[int] = @[]): seq[ScaleValue]

  
Facet = object
  columns*: seq[string]

Draw = object
  fname*: string
  width*: Option[float]
  height*: Option[float]

VegaDraw = object
  nil

BinPositionKind = enum
  bpNone = "none", bpCenter = "center", bpLeft = "left", bpRight = "right"
GeomKind = enum
  gkPoint, gkBar, gkHistogram, gkFreqPoly, gkTile, gkLine
Geom = object
  gid*: uint16
  data*: Option[DataFrame]
  style*: Option[Style]
  position*: PositionKind
  aes*: Aesthetics
  binPosition*: BinPositionKind
  kind*: GeomKind
  case statKind*: StatKind
  of stBin:
      numBins*: int
      binWidth*: Option[float]
      binEdges*: Option[seq[float]]

  else:
      nil

  
Theme = object
  xlabel*: Option[string]
  xlabelMargin*: Option[float]
  ylabel*: Option[string]
  ylabelMargin*: Option[float]
  xLabelSecondary*: Option[string]
  yLabelSecondary*: Option[string]
  legendPosition*: Option[Coord]
  discreteScaleMargin*: Option[Quantity]

GgPlot[T] = object
  data*: T
  title*: string
  subtitle*: string
  aes*: Aesthetics
  numXticks*: int
  numYticks*: int
  facet*: Option[Facet]
  geoms*: seq[Geom]
  theme*: Theme

FilledGeom = object
  geom*: Geom
  xcol*: string
  ycol*: string
  xScale*: ginger.Scale
  yScale*: ginger.Scale
  yieldData*: OrderedTable[Style, (seq[Style], DataFrame)]
  dcKindX*: DiscreteKind
  dcKindY*: DiscreteKind
  numX*: int
  numY*: int

MainAddScales = tuple[main: Option[Scale], more: seq[Scale]]
FilledScales = object
  xScale*: ginger.Scale
  yScale*: ginger.Scale
  geoms*: seq[FilledGeom]
  x*: MainAddScales
  y*: MainAddScales
  color*: MainAddScales
  fill*: MainAddScales
  size*: MainAddScales
  shape*: MainAddScales

PlotView = object
  filledScales*: FilledScales
  view*: Viewport
